column2: SELECT up_id,  dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq( up_ra,up_dec,up_sep ) as objId   FROM #upload  WHERE  dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq( up_ra,up_dec,up_sep ) IS NOT NULL  SELECT TOP #   p.ra,p.dec, cast(str(p.ra,#,#) as float) as ra,cast(str(p.[dec],#,#) as float) as dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,p.modelMagErr_u,p.modelMagErr_g,p.modelMagErr_r,p.modelMagErr_i,p.modelMagErr_z,dbo.fIAUFromEq(p.ra,p.[dec]) as SDSSname,p.err_g,p.err_i,p.err_r,p.err_u,p.err_z,p.modelMag_g,p.modelMag_i,p.modelMag_r,p.modelMag_u,p.modelMag_z  FROM ..PhotoObj AS p  JOIN #x AS x ON x.objID=p.objID  JOIN #upload AS u ON u.up_id = x.up_id   WHERE  ( p.type = # OR p.type = #)   ORDER BY x.up_id
